         <abstract id="aspace_96fff7a4eba209a02678c7838631c36c">Seventy-three black and white photographs of the Jewish community in Radauti, Romania, taken between 1976-1978. Shown are portraits of individuals, street scenes, and photographs of Jewish ceremonial occasions. Exhibition catalogues (1978-1980) are also included.</abstract>
         <origination label="creator">
            <persname identifier="http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/n79100439"
                      rules="aacr"
                      source="naf">
               <part>Salzmann, Laurence</part>
            </persname>
         </origination>
    
      </did>
